    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>A sheen of warding sweat blunts the next searing blow.</em></p><p><strong>Reaction when you take acid/cold/fire/lightning/thunder damage: resistance to that damage this turn, and +1d6 of that type on your next melee hit.</strong></p><hr/><p><strong>Ashen:</strong> <strong>Tier 1 pyromancy</strong> — <strong>2 casts per bonfire</strong> (refills on a long rest); your school's 15 milestone adds +1. Gated by the Pyromancy Flame; requires a <strong>Pyromancy Flame</strong> in hand. Based on SRD <em>Absorb Elements</em>.</p>",
